  "gui.transmutatoria.alchemy_slot.description.normal": "Reacts according to the base essence relation. A matching essence annihilates and reveals the slot.",
  "gui.transmutatoria.alchemy_slot.description.deterioration": "After the base reaction, deteriorates the essence once and increases crucible polarity by 1.",
  "gui.transmutatoria.alchemy_slot.description.activation": "After the base reaction, activates the essence once and decreases crucible polarity by 1.",
  "gui.transmutatoria.alchemy_slot.description.inversion": "Reverses the base reaction's activation or deterioration effect, along with its crucible-polarity change.",
  "gui.transmutatoria.alchemy_slot.description.diffusion": "After reacting, passes this slot's activation or deterioration effect to every adjacent produced, uninhibited essence. Its polarity change is applied once for this slot and once for each successful diffusion.",
